foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: Please note that BOEM and BSEE appear for the first time in this report. On October 1, 2011, the Bureau of Ocean Energy Management, Regulation and Enforcement (BOEMRE), itself formerly the Minerals Management Service (MMS), was replaced by BOEM and BSEE as part of a major reorganization.
Increased auditing and training in FY12 has lead DOI to conclude that the numbers reported last year were in slight need of adjusting. The numbers in this column represent the adjusted FY11 numbers.
